<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>AFC 01903 - Replacement Rear Engine Mount Snubber Washer Used on 4300 and 4400 Models with VIN Numbers
        before 2H411832 Built Between October 24, 2000 and March 21, 2001
    </stitle>
    <afc id="afc01903">
        <afcnum>01903</afcnum>
        <afcdate>June, 2001</afcdate>
        <subjectfile>ENGINE</subjectfile>
        <subject>Replacement Rear Engine Mount Snubber Washer Used on 4300 and 4400 Models with VIN Numbers before
            2H411832 Built Between October 24, 2000 and March 21, 2001
        </subject>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>4300
                    <daterange>
                        <startdate>10/24/2000</startdate>
                        <enddate>03/21/2001</enddate>
                    </daterange>
                </truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4400
                    <daterange>
                        <startdate>10/24/2000</startdate>
                        <enddate>03/21/2001</enddate>
                    </daterange>
                </truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <exhotlnk document="../afcs/AFC01903.pdf" bookname="AFC">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the AFC
                        letter
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
                <para>The rear engine mounts on 4300 and 4400 Models built between October 24, 2000 and March 21, 2001
                    have the wrong snubber washer installed. The integrity of the engine mount is maintained but the
                    vehicle will exhibit greater mirror vibration at engine idle, floor vibration, increased low
                    frequency interior noise levels and premature isolator wear.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
